import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['u'], data['v'])
    plt.title('What is the overall distribution of the 2D points?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('u')
    plt.ylabel('v')
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.xticks(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['u'], data['v'])
    plt.plot(np.unique(data['u']), np.poly1d(np.polyfit(data['u'], data['v'], 1))(np.unique(data['u'])), color='red')
    plt.title('What is the correlation between u and v?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('u')
    plt.ylabel('v')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    x = data['u']
    y = data['v']
    heatmap, xedges, yedges = np.histogram2d(x, y, bins=50)
    extent = [xedges[0], xedges[-1], yedges[0], yedges[-1]]
    plt.imshow(heatmap.T, extent=extent, origin='lower')
    plt.colorbar()
    plt.title('Are there any clusters or patterns in the data?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('u')
    plt.ylabel('v')
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
